title: #139 - The Rolling Stone Magazine article "The Undergraduate"
description: I read the Rolling Stone article written about about me in 1997 titled The Undergraduate in which I was titled The #1 Party Animal in the Country...this is the article that changed my life. I am a bad out loud reader so beware of spirals!
